data.database_description: This database manages customer information, orders, invoices, financial transactions, and product details for an e-commerce business. It tracks customers' accounts, order history, transaction records, and product categories, ensuring comprehensive management of sales and financial activities while maintaining detailed product information. The interconnected tables support efficient data retrieval and reporting across various aspects of the business operations.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each customer.
First name of the customer.
Middle initial of the customer.
Last name of the customer.
Gender identifier for the customer (1 for male, 0 for female).
Email address of the customer.
Username used by the customer for login.
Password used by the customer for login.
Phone number of the customer.
Town or city where the customer resides.
State, county, or province where the customer resides.
Country where the customer resides.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores detailed customer information for e-commerce business management.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each order.
Identifier linking the order to a specific customer.
Date and time when the order was placed.
Details of the products ordered.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Records details of orders placed by customers.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each invoice.
References the order for which the invoice was generated.
Date and time when the invoice was created.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores information about invoices generated for orders.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each account.
Identifier linking the account to a specific customer.
Date when the account was opened.
Name or code assigned to the account.
Additional details about the account.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores information about customer accounts, including account details and account opening date.

columns.columnDescription: Unique code identifying each product category.
Description of the product category.
VAT (Value Added Tax) rate applicable to the product category.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores information about different product categories, including VAT ratings.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each product.
Identifier for the parent product if applicable (used for related products).
Code linking the product to its category in the Product_Categories table.
Price of a single unit of the product.
Name of the product.
Color of the product.
Size of the product.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Contains details about individual products, including pricing and categorization.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each transaction.
Identifier linking the transaction to a specific account.
Number referencing the invoice associated with the transaction.
Type of transaction, such as Payment or Refund.
Date when the transaction occurred.
Amount involved in the transaction.
Comment describing the transaction.
Additional details about the transaction.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Records all financial transactions related to accounts, including transaction type and amount.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each item in an order.
Identifier linking the item to its respective order.
Identifier linking the item to its respective product.
Quantity of the product ordered.
Additional details about the order item.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores details about individual items within orders, including product information and quantities.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for the order item.
Identifier for the invoice associated with this line item.
Unique identifier for the product being invoiced.
Title or name of the product.
Quantity of the product included in this line item.
Price of a single unit of the product.
Calculated cost of the product based on its price and quantity.
Value-added tax (VAT) amount calculated for this line item.
Total cost including VAT, representing the final amount due for this line item.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Contains detailed information about each item on an invoice, including product details and financial calculations.
